{"tid":1803829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗官玩嘢，比擔保外出但每日要報到兩次，簡直折磨","createTime":"2019-12-30T13:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T14:03:40.000Z","uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29af603f83c7909ad7cb4881e64377261710edfb","tid":1803829,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"兩名學生被指於上月23日區議會選舉前夕凌晨時分，在粉嶺華心邨的「姚銘區議員辦事處」縱火，以損毀該辦事處。案中被控縱火的27歲明愛專上學院學生李欣樺，自今年11月被捕後還押至今1個多月，他今早(30日)獲高院法官李運騰批准以現金3萬港元保釋。<br />\n法官下令他保釋期間須遵守一系列條件，包括不得離境、每晚11時至清晨6時須守宵禁令、不得騷擾控方證人，以及每日到警署報到兩次，報到時間為每日中午12時至下午2時，及晚上8時至10時。<br />\n此外，法官考慮他仍然在學，安排他周一至周五中午在他所讀院校附近的將軍澳警署報到，晚上才在他住址附近的上水警署報到；至於周末周日及公眾假期均在上水警署報到。<br />\n<br />\nCLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1de5c698383bd25efab5e01847872d27c71023","tid":1803829,"uid":48318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[極限挑戰] <span style=\"color: red;\">德國第三份聯署，最後48小時</span>，要多3萬人，連登仔做唔做到?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803447</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkawvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=6fa1c6a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7231498a7a39ece2c72864b9e2ff77d10b3e64f5","tid":1803829,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"Diu"},{"pid":"061c9234522a2cefc403a10eed2cc3109ac11aac","tid":1803829,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:03:40.000Z","